      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable and well-presented daily driver. The exterior paint retains a beautiful shine, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a small hairline scratch near the trunk\u2014typical signs of careful use. The alloy wheels are in great shape with no significant curb rash. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the leather seats remain firm and supportive, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic component, from the heated seats to the infotainment system, functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is dry and runs quietly, benefiting from a documented history of on-time oil changes and a recent coolant flush. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This car drives straight and true, offering a smooth ride that reflects its well-cared-for history.",
